        "html": "<p style=\"text-align: center\">In 2014, Aman Gupta and Sameer Mehta entered a world of unsailed waters to birth fashionable, affordable and quality audio products and accessories for India’s evolving youth. The passion and grit of young millennials and Gen-Z asked for products that could compliment their hustle and empower them in their journey. And that’s exactly why we’re here.\n<\/p>",
